# ‚úÖ **AVIS HEADER: CY_HY_CONST**

```php
/*=====================================================================
    AIFVS-ARTIFACT: CY_HY_CONST
    AVIS-ID: COPILOT_CMS.CONST.CY_HY_CONST
    AVIS-PATH: HTDOCS/PHP/COPILOT_CMS/CONST/CY_HY_CONST.php
    AVIS-TYPE: CONSTANT-REGISTRY
    AVIS-DESCRIPTION:
        Canonical HTML constant registry for COPILOT_CMS.
        Provides immutable, deterministic, AVIS-law compliant constants
        for HTML symbols, tokens, and element tags.
    AVIS-VERSION: 1.0.0
    AVIS-AUTHOR: Demon
    AVIS-LAW:
        - Immutable constants only
        - No logic, no rendering
        - Deterministic output
        - Self-identifying artifact
=====================================================================*/
```

