# ‚úÖ **AVIS HEADER: LLM_LOADER**

```php
/*=====================================================================
    AIFVS-ARTIFACT: LLM_LOADER
    AVIS-ID: COPILOT_CMS.CONST.LLM_LOADER
    AVIS-PATH: HTDOCS/PHP/COPILOT_CMS/CONST/LLM_LOADER.php
    AVIS-TYPE: LOADER
    AVIS-DESCRIPTION:
        Primary loader for COPILOT_CMS LLM generator environment.
        Loads AVIS debug constants FIRST, then core constant registries.
        Establishes deterministic include order for generator systems.
    AVIS-VERSION: 1.1.0
    AVIS-AUTHOR: Demon
    AVIS-LAW:
        - Debug constants MUST load before all others
        - Loader performs no logic and no mutation
        - Deterministic include order is mandatory
        - Self-identifying artifact
=====================================================================*/
```

