    AVIS-VERSION: 1.0.0
    AVIS-AUTHOR: Demon
    AVIS-LAW:
        - phpinfo() MUST NOT be executed
        - Only identifiers may be defined
        - No dynamic values, no environment reads
        - Deterministic, immutable, self-identifying artifact
=====================================================================*/
```

